
### Mayonnaise



### Texas Mayonnaise
### p. 125

* 1 egg
* 1 t Dijon mustard or 1/2 t dry mustard
* 3 T fresh lemon juice or vinegar
* 1/2 t salt
* 1/2 t red pepper
* 1/2 cup corn oil
* 1/2 cup olive oil

* Combine egg, mustard, lemon juice, herbs, salt, pepper in a blender
* With blender running, slowly add oils until mayo is thick
* add more lemon juice if desired



### Pyles p. 46

* 2 egg yolks
* 3/4 tsp salt
* pepper to taste
* 1 tsp Dijon mustard
* 1/2 cup veg oil
* 1/2 cup EVOO
* 2 tsp lemon juice
* 1/4-1/2 cup chicken stock or water

* whisk together egg yolks, salt, pepper, mustard
* combine oils and drizzle into bowl while whisking until thoroughly incorporated
* add lemon juice
